Re-check a destination: existence and size for every restore point's closure. Exits nonzero when verification fails

Usage: sleet mirror verify [OPTIONS] <ROOT> <DB> <TARGET>

Arguments:
  <ROOT>
          Fleet root URL, e.g. s3://ops/sleet/

  <DB>
          Registered database URL

  <TARGET>
          Mirror target name

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format

          Possible values:
          - text: Human-readable text
          - json: JSON matching the subcommand's response schema
          
          [default: text]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
